  title: "What\u2019s the benefit of using a `shootPoint` GameObject?"
  text: The `shootPoint` defines the exact location on the turret head where bullets
    should spawn. This is more flexible than guessing coordinates and ensures bullets
    fire from the correct position, even if the head rotates.
